juni 17, 2020

Load data

load("partisan_geotracking_data_file.rda")

Distance Analyses

Time validation

fit_dat <- 
  d[, c("daily_distance_diff", 
        "time_day_linear" , "time_day_quad",
        "county_fips", "state_name")]
fit_dat <- 
  fit_dat[complete.cases(fit_dat),]

timer <- Sys.time()
fit_dist_time_valid <-
  lmer(
    daily_distance_diff ~ 1 + time_day_linear + time_day_quad + 
      (1 | county_fips) + 
      (1 + (time_day_linear + time_day_quad) | state_name),
    data = fit_dat,
    control = lmerControl(optimizer = "bobyqa")
    
  )
Sys.time()-timer

save(fit_dist_time_valid,
     file = paste0("model_files/", "LMER_fit_dist_time_valid.rda"))
tab_model(fit_dist_time_valid, 
          digits = 3, digits.re = 3)

#pdf("two_panel_just_time.pdf", width = 8, height = 4)
par(mfrow=c(1,2), mar = c(3,3,2,0), oma = c(1,3,2,5))

plotdat <- get_plot_dat(model = fit_dist_final_valid,
                        data = fit_dat )

plot_data_with_sims(fit_dat = fit_dat,
                    plotdat = plotdat,
                    y_var = "daily_distance_diff",
                    y_label = "",
                    main_label = "Reduction in Overall Movement")

plotdat <- get_plot_dat(model = fit_visit_final_valid,
                        data = fit_dat_V)

plot_data_with_sims(fit_dat = fit_dat_V,
                    plotdat = plotdat,
                    y_var = "daily_visitation_diff",
                    y_label = "",
                    main_label = "Reduction in Visiting Non-Essential Services")

mtext("Date", 1, 0, outer = T, font = 2, cex = 0.8)
mtext("Physical distancing: \n% Reduction in Overall Movement \n and Visiting Non-Essential Services",
      2, 0, outer = T, font = 2, cex = 0.7)
